1969
1970void WebAutomationSession::performInteractionSequence(const Inspector::Protocol::Automation::BrowsingContextHandle& handle, const Inspector::Protocol::Automation::FrameHandle& frameHandle, Ref<JSON::Array>&& inputSources, Ref<JSON::Array>&& steps, Ref<WebAutomationSession::PerformInteractionSequenceCallback>&& callback)
1971{
1972 // This command implements WebKit support for ยง17.5 Perform Actions.
1973
1974#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_ACTIONS_API)
1975 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(NotImplemented);
1976#else
1977 WebPageProxy* page = webPageProxyForHandle(handle);
1978 if (!page)
1979 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(WindowNotFound);
1980
1981 bool frameNotFound = false;
1982 auto frameID = webFrameIDForHandle(frameHandle, frameNotFound);
1983 if (frameNotFound)
1984 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(FrameNotFound);
1985
1986 // Parse and validate Automation protocol arguments. By this point, the driver has
1987 // already performed the steps in ยง17.3 Processing Actions Requests.
1988 if (!inputSources->length())
1989 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "The parameter 'inputSources' was not found or empty.");
1990
1991 HashSet<String> sourceIdSet;
1992 for (const auto& inputSourceValue : inputSources.get()) {
1993 auto inputSourceObject = inputSourceValue->asObject();
1994 if (!inputSourceObject)
1995 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "An input source in the 'inputSources' parameter was invalid.");
1996
1997 auto sourceId = inputSourceObject->getString("sourceId"_s);
1998 if (!sourceId)
1999 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "An input source in the 'inputSources' parameter is missing a 'sourceId'.");
2000
2001 auto sourceType = inputSourceObject->getString("sourceType"_s);
2002 if (!sourceType)
2003 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "An input source in the 'inputSources' parameter is missing a 'sourceType'.");
2004
2005 auto parsedInputSourceType = Inspector::Protocol::AutomationHelpers::parseEnumValueFromString<Inspector::Protocol::Automation::InputSourceType>(sourceType);
2006 if (!parsedInputSourceType)
2007 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "An input source in the 'inputSources' parameter has an invalid 'sourceType'.");
2008
2009 SimulatedInputSourceType inputSourceType = simulatedInputSourceTypeFromProtocolSourceType(*parsedInputSourceType);
2010
2011 // Note: iOS does not support mouse input sources, and other platforms do not support touch input sources.
2012 // If a mismatch happens, alias to the supported input source. This works because both Mouse and Touch input sources
2013 // use a MouseButton to indicate the result of interacting (down/up/move), which can be interpreted for touch or mouse.
2014#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_MOUSE_INTERACTIONS) && ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_TOUCH_INTERACTIONS)
2015 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Mouse || inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Pen)
2016 inputSourceType = SimulatedInputSourceType::Touch;
2017#elif ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_MOUSE_INTERACTIONS) && !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_TOUCH_INTERACTIONS)
2018 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Touch)
2019 inputSourceType = SimulatedInputSourceType::Mouse;
2020#endif
2021#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_MOUSE_INTERACTIONS)
2022 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Mouse)
2023 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(NotImplemented, "Mouse input sources are not yet supported.");
2024 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Pen)
2025 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(NotImplemented, "Pen input sources are not yet supported.");
2026#endif
2027#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_TOUCH_INTERACTIONS)
2028 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Touch)
2029 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(NotImplemented, "Touch input sources are not yet supported.");
2030#endif
2031#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_KEYBOARD_INTERACTIONS)
2032 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Keyboard)
2033 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(NotImplemented, "Keyboard input sources are not yet supported.");
2034#endif
2035#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_WHEEL_INTERACTIONS)
2036 if (inputSourceType == SimulatedInputSourceType::Wheel)
2037 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(NotImplemented, "Wheel input sources are not yet supported.");
2038#endif
2039 if (sourceIdSet.contains(sourceId))
2040 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Two input sources with the same sourceId were specified.");
2041
2042 sourceIdSet.add(sourceId);
2043 m_inputSources.ensure(sourceId, [inputSourceType] {
2044 return SimulatedInputSource::create(inputSourceType);
2045 });
2046 }
2047
2048 Vector<SimulatedInputKeyFrame> keyFrames;
2049
2050 if (!steps->length())
2051 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "The parameter 'steps' was not found or empty.");
2052
2053 for (const auto& stepValue : steps.get()) {
2054 auto stepObject = stepValue->asObject();
2055 if (!stepObject)
2056 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "A step in the 'steps' parameter was not an object.");
2057
2058 auto stepStates = stepObject->getArray("states"_s);
2059 if (!stepStates)
2060 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "A step is missing the 'states' property.");
2061
2062 Vector<SimulatedInputKeyFrame::StateEntry> entries;
2063 entries.reserveCapacity(stepStates->length());
2064
2065 for (const auto& stateValue : *stepStates) {
2066 auto stateObject = stateValue->asObject();
2067 if (!stateObject)
2068 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Encountered a non-object step state.");
2069
2070 auto sourceId = stateObject->getString("sourceId"_s);
2071 if (!sourceId)
2072 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Step state lacks required 'sourceId' property.");
2073
2074 if (!m_inputSources.contains(sourceId))
2075 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Unknown 'sourceId' specified.");
2076
2077 SimulatedInputSource& inputSource = *m_inputSources.get(sourceId);
2078 SimulatedInputSourceState sourceState { };
2079
2080 auto pressedCharKeyString = stateObject->getString("pressedCharKey"_s);
2081 if (!!pressedCharKeyString) {
2082 auto charKey = pressedCharKey(pressedCharKeyString);
2083 if (!charKey)
2084 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Invalid 'pressedCharKey'.");
2085 sourceState.pressedCharKeys.add(*charKey);
2086 }
2087
2088 if (auto pressedVirtualKeysArray = stateObject->getArray("pressedVirtualKeys"_s)) {
2089 VirtualKeyMap pressedVirtualKeys;
2090
2091 for (auto it = pressedVirtualKeysArray->begin(); it != pressedVirtualKeysArray->end(); ++it) {
2092 auto pressedVirtualKeyString = (*it)->asString();
2093 if (!pressedVirtualKeyString)
2094 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Encountered a non-string virtual key value.");
2095
2096 std::optional<VirtualKey> parsedVirtualKey = Inspector::Protocol::AutomationHelpers::parseEnumValueFromString<Inspector::Protocol::Automation::VirtualKey>(pressedVirtualKeyString);
2097 if (!parsedVirtualKey)
2098 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Encountered an unknown virtual key value.");
2099 else
2100 pressedVirtualKeys.add(normalizedVirtualKey(parsedVirtualKey.value()), parsedVirtualKey.value());
2101 }
2102
2103 sourceState.pressedVirtualKeys = pressedVirtualKeys;
2104 }
2105
2106 auto pressedButtonString = stateObject->getString("pressedButton"_s);
2107 if (!!pressedButtonString) {
2108 auto protocolButton = Inspector::Protocol::AutomationHelpers::parseEnumValueFromString<Inspector::Protocol::Automation::MouseButton>(pressedButtonString);
2109 sourceState.pressedMouseButton = protocolButton.value_or(MouseButton::None);
2110 }
2111
2112 auto originString = stateObject->getString("origin"_s);
2113 if (!!originString)
2114 sourceState.origin = Inspector::Protocol::AutomationHelpers::parseEnumValueFromString<Inspector::Protocol::Automation::MouseMoveOrigin>(originString);
2115
2116 if (sourceState.origin && sourceState.origin.value() == Inspector::Protocol::Automation::MouseMoveOrigin::Element) {
2117 auto nodeHandleString = stateObject->getString("nodeHandle"_s);
2118 if (!nodeHandleString)
2119 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InvalidParameter, "Node handle not provided for 'Element' origin");
2120 sourceState.nodeHandle = nodeHandleString;
2121 }
2122
2123 if (auto locationObject = stateObject->getObject("location"_s)) {
2124 auto x = locationObject->getInteger("x"_s);
2125 auto y = locationObject->getInteger("y"_s);
2126 if (x && y)
2127 sourceState.location = WebCore::IntPoint(*x, *y);
2128 }
2129
2130 if (auto deltaObject = stateObject->getObject("delta"_s)) {
2131 auto deltaX = deltaObject->getInteger("width"_s);
2132 auto deltaY = deltaObject->getInteger("height"_s);
2133 if (deltaX && deltaY)
2134 sourceState.scrollDelta = WebCore::IntSize(*deltaX, *deltaY);
2135 }
2136
2137 if (auto duration = stateObject->getInteger("duration"_s))
2138 sourceState.duration = Seconds::fromMilliseconds(*duration);
2139
2140 entries.uncheckedAppend(std::pair<SimulatedInputSource&, SimulatedInputSourceState> { inputSource, sourceState });
2141 }
2142
2143 keyFrames.append(SimulatedInputKeyFrame(WTFMove(entries)));
2144 }
2145
2146 SimulatedInputDispatcher& inputDispatcher = inputDispatcherForPage(*page);
2147 if (inputDispatcher.isActive()) {
2148 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2149 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR_AND_DETAILS(InternalError, "A previous interaction is still underway.");
2150 }
2151
2152 // Delegate the rest of ยง17.4 Dispatching Actions to the dispatcher.
2153 inputDispatcher.run(frameID, WTFMove(keyFrames), m_inputSources, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), callback = WTFMove(callback)](std::optional<AutomationCommandError> error) {
2154 if (error)
2155 callback->sendFailure(error.value().toProtocolString());
2156 else
2157 callback->sendSuccess();
2158 });
2159#endif // ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_ACTIONS_API)
2160}
2161
2162void WebAutomationSession::cancelInteractionSequence(const Inspector::Protocol::Automation::BrowsingContextHandle& handle, const Inspector::Protocol::Automation::FrameHandle& frameHandle, Ref<CancelInteractionSequenceCallback>&& callback)
2163{
2164 // This command implements WebKit support for ยง17.6 Release Actions.
2165
2166#if !ENABLE(WEBDRIVER_ACTIONS_API)
2167 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(NotImplemented);
2168#else
2169 WebPageProxy* page = webPageProxyForHandle(handle);
2170 if (!page)
2171 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(WindowNotFound);
2172
2173 bool frameNotFound = false;
2174 auto frameID = webFrameIDForHandle(frameHandle, frameNotFound);
2175 if (frameNotFound)
2176 ASYNC_FAIL_WITH_PREDEFINED_ERROR(FrameNotFound);
2177
2178 Vector<SimulatedInputKeyFrame> keyFrames({ SimulatedInputKeyFrame::keyFrameToResetInputSources(m_inputSources) });
